Klasse NoneStructureModifier

net.minecraftforge.common.world.NoneStructureModifier
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
StructureModifier
public class NoneStructureModifier extends Object implements StructureModifier
Noop structure modifier. Can be used in a structure modifier json with "type": "forge:none". intended for datapack makers who want to disable a structure modifier
